==English==
===Etymology===
Compare with French [[appréciable]].

===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] //

===Adjective===
# Capable of being appreciated or estimated; large enough to be estimated; perceptible; as, an appreciable quantity.&mdash;

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[havaittava]], [[huomattava]]

=== Adverb ===
'''appreciably'''
# in an appreciable manner

